Derivation / Comments / Predecessor:
Abbreviated form of PRCAT to simplify programming and data checks.
If PR.PRCAT in ('CONCOMITANT AND SUBSEQUENT LOCAL RADIATION THERAPY', 'HISTORY OF LOCAL RADIATION THERAPY') then set to 'Radiation Therapy';
If PRCAT in ('CONCOMITANT/SUBSEQUENT SURGERY AND PROCS', 'HISTORY OF SURGERIES AND PROCEDURES') then set to 'Surgery/Procedures'
If PRCAT = 'IMAGING DETAILS' then ACAT1 = 'Imaging Details'; 
If PRCAT = 'PRIOR AND CONCOMITANT TRANSFUSIONS' then ACAT1= 'Transfusion'.

If PRTRT starts with the text 'EBRT', then set to "EBRT";
If PRTRT = 'BRACHYTHERAPY' then set to "Internal Radiation Therapy (Brachytherapy)";
If PRTRT = 'RADIOEMBOLIZATION' then set to "Radioembolization";
If PRTRT starts with the text "OTHER" then set to "Other";
Otherwise, set to PRTRT.
